# {{PROJECT_NAME}}

> Ubiquitous-language glossary for this project. Inspired by Eric Evans, *Domain-Driven Design*. Inspired in form by mattpocock/skills.
>
> **Rules of this file**:
> - Only terms that are meaningful to domain experts (i.e. the user, customers, or business stakeholders). Not implementation details.
> - Every term is canonical. List rejected synonyms under `*Avoid*` so the agent can challenge drift.
> - Add to this file lazily, as terms come up in `/grill-with-docs` or `/plan-feature` sessions. Don't pre-author a full dictionary upfront.
> - When new information contradicts an existing entry, log it in `## Flagged ambiguities`, don't overwrite.

